91
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:03,590
that he erected?

92
00:06:03,590 --> 00:06:08,750
We might assume that the historian would be after a history of patronage,

93
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:09,730
for example.

94
00:06:09,730 --> 00:06:14,630
