134
00:08:43,789 --> 00:08:45,440
He takes away the side wings.

135
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:49,230
He takes away the poche, the scale, everything, in other words,

136
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:53,030
that Palladio indicates in his plan and elevation.

137
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:56,090
We want to think about how these diagrams give us

138
00:08:56,090 --> 00:09:01,880
a certain highly particular view of the Renaissance, which privileges geometry,

139
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:07,130
all the way from its basic spatial units to the general order given

140
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:09,880
to the universe by God.

